    {
      "id": "PopularPost187722",
      "post_content": "you know, I know 'great with X reducer effects' arguments aren't encouraged, since you might as well say 'great with Black Lotus' and have done with it--  \n  \nbut honestly, I could see myself running 4x this, 4x Sol Ring in a casual deck, and feel safe running only basic lands. this speaks more to the mighty power of The Ring than to the value of this card, but you have to admit- that is a tempting effect to try to get use out of- mutiple colored mana, card draw, and an artifact going to the graveyard?   \n  \nI can't believe it's not broken.",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
