    {
      "id": "PopularPost332546",
      "post_content": "It's temporary mana-accel that draws you a card AND color fixes; that has to be OK in some decks. Drop T3 in black, cantrip into a [Bloodgift demon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodgift demon); who will start drawing you cards (which is great!)  \n  \nIt can give you tempo if you control it; but you only want to see 1 at a time; so I'd say a 2-of in a deck that wants to try it out.",
      "posted_by": "blurrymadness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost332546\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">It's temporary mana-accel that draws you a card AND color fixes; that has to be OK in some decks. Drop T3 in black, cantrip into a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bloodgift demon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodgift demon\">Bloodgift demon</a>; who will start drawing you cards (which is great!)<br/><br/>It can give you tempo if you control it; but you only want to see 1 at a time; so I'd say a 2-of in a deck that wants to try it out.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '332546'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44651\">blurrymadness</span>\r\n                                (7/30/2013 9:13:09 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src